race.description: Hyoketsu Lawn Party On Sale Handicap (C3)
race.comment: HEZANGELIC (4) is a leader busting to win. Went close in stronger class this track/trip last time and he can control the race from the inside barrier. The 3kg claim brings him right into it. EARL IT IS (6) spiked his figures, just missing a place here this trip when well supported. Has delivered the Maiden win prior and has turned the corner. Presents fitter and the 2kg claim is handy. SO IMMACULATE (11) led and won that race and went close at Geraldton following. Presents on a 7-day backup and will carry just 51.5kg with Cheung's claim. Has winning claims if she can cross economically from the awkward gate. JUST GIFTED (10) peaks and is a capable mare who can't be ruled out despite coming back to a short sprint.
